{"tid":1300160,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人中過外耳炎 (swimmer's ear) ?","createTime":"2019-07-09T09:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T10:14:32.000Z","uid":18729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"85592d593b13ecb4418e39f22e5710797f12d80f","tid":1300160,"uid":18729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:36:36.000Z","msg":"之前耳痛睇醫生<br />\n醫生話耳入面有一粒瘡發炎有膿<br />\n開左支ear drop (dexatrol) 俾我滴<br />\n<br />\n而家過左個prescribed既療期(1 week)停用左<br />\n隻耳都冇再痛冇痕癢冇耳塞<br />\n聽野都清楚<br />\n但仲有一個問題<br />\n就係成日覺得隻耳入面好濕<br />\n好似有啲液體係入面咁<br />\n但用紙巾又唔見濕<br />\n又唔覺有水自動流出黎<br />\n呢段時間亦都好小心冇俾水入耳<br />\n<br />\n如果情況再係咁會去覆診<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人都曾經患過外耳炎<br />\n想問咁既情況係咪正常?"},{"pid":"42323f8904f87e0cadfbcac86cf8790b8c7f8a1e","tid":1300160,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"咁去覆診，醫生講咩。"},{"pid":"a9e5363dc42bed5d02e5ce6c0a94c4b78bcfc061","tid":1300160,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:43:48.000Z","msg":"借個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u6Lb70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u6Lb70.png&h=84e8e474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14/7 已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dgrcBT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dgrcBT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9158c4e8d473aa5f0ba9e30c0e55ad96e1fc038","tid":1300160,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:49:22.000Z","msg":"左右耳都長期岀水<br />\n唔夠瞓會塞<br />\n無睇過醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641e6bf0d04177ed0433cf5fe1601d37f8947410","tid":1300160,"uid":18729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42323f8904f87e0cadf